moonglow: High-level interface to OpenGL+FreeGLUT for LuaJIT

On Ubuntu 16.04, I need to do the following:

 $ export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/usr/lib/nvidia-340

Otherwise, I'm getting:

 libGL error: No matching fbConfigs or visuals found
 libGL error: failed to load driver: swrast


To try out:

 $ ./testglow.lua
 $ ./lunart.lua <Duke3D *.ART files...>
 $ ./depthfight.sh
